item.title: Food and habits
item.description: Tough topic.I know you probably don’t agree. Me neither.I don’t even agree with myself, I’m not asking you to agree with my contradicting self. I want to tackle this “problem” in the most logic, clear and hopefully concise manner.But first we need to put…Definitions! Heroes that always save the day. A value is a fairly abstract concept. the regard that something is held to deserve; the importance, worth, or usefulness of something.
